casebody.data:
Edith Kane, Respondent v. The Metropolitan Elevated Railway Company, et al., Appellants. Decided December 17, 1891. Appeal by defendants' from judgment entered upon decision of judge at equity term. Davies & Rapallo, attorneys, and J. C. Thomson of counsel, for appellants. John A. Weekes, Jr., for respondent.

Before McAdam and Gildersleeve, JJ.

Per Curiam.

Judgment affirmed, with costs.
